# X2Mail Commit Message Convention
# ─────────────────────────────────
# Format: <type>: <short description>
#
# Types:
#   feat     New feature or capability
#   fix      Bug fix
#   docs     Documentation only
#   refactor Code change that neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature
#   style    Formatting, missing semicolons, etc (no code change)
#   test     Adding or updating tests
#   build    Build system, CI, dependencies
#   release  Version bump and release prep
#
# Rules:
#   - Subject line: max 72 chars, lowercase after type
#   - Body: explain WHY, not WHAT (the diff shows what)
#   - Blank line between subject and body
#   - Reference issues: Fixes #123, Closes #456
#   - NO Co-Authored-By or AI references
#
# Team: NKIT Dev (https://github.com/NK-IT-CLOUD)
# Repo: https://github.com/NK-IT-CLOUD/x2mail
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add occ x2mail:setup command with preflight checks
#   fix: DomainConfigService writes full SM domain config format
#   docs: add Dovecot OAUTHBEARER setup guide to README
#   release: v0.2.0
